\c 64
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira kudzivirirwa pavavengi
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Inzwai inzwi rangu, Mwari, pachichemo changu; chengetedzai upenyu hwangu pakutya muvengi.
\v 2 Ndivanzei pazano rakavanda rakaipa revakaipa; pabope revaiti vezvakaipa,
\v 3 vakarodza rurimi rwavo semunondo, vakashumba miseve yavo, \add iwo\add* mashoko anovava.
\v 4 Kufura wakarurama vari pakuvanda; kamwe-kamwe vanomufura, vasingatyi.
\v 5 Vanozvisimbisa panyaya yakaipa; vanorondedzera zvekuteya misungo pakavanda; vanoti: Ndiani angaiona?
\v 6 Vanotsvakisisa zvitadzo; \add vanoti\add*: Tagadzirira nezano rakavanzwa neunyengeri; mufungo wemunhu wechemukati pamwe nemoyo zvakadzika.
\p
\v 7 Asi Mwari achavafura \add ne\add*museve, mavanga avo achakurumidza.
\v 8 Zvino vachawisira rurimi rwavo pamusoro pavo; vese vanovaona vachatiza.
\v 9 Zvino vanhu vese vachatya; uye vachaparidza basa raMwari, uye kuita kwake vachicherekedza.
\v 10 Vakarurama vachafara muna Jehovha, uye vachavimba naye; uye vese vakachena pamoyo vachazvikudza.
